{"tid":786373,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無之中睇返以前個ex send比我既message, 個心那住","createTime":"2018-08-20T01:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:47:14.000Z","uid":106019,"like":74,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8058fa3f2dc9ea68ad11de7b8d1926b405bf3b69","tid":786373,"uid":106019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"琴日因為某d原因要搵返以前既野，咁我用盡曬方法搵，但無意中睇到個msg搞到我成晚訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大約十年前我識左佢，我當時覺得佢好靚，唔覺得自己溝到呢d女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地好神奇地好快就一齊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊果段時間雖然唔長，但都好開心<br />\n<br />\n我當時因為要去外國讀書，去之前無耐就飛左佢，原因係當時細個，覺得去外國大把女就飛左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住咁多年黎都無見過<br />\n<br />\n琴晚睇返個msg, 係我去外國前send比我，好似覺得完全無睇過咁，可能當時根本完全唔care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 內容大致上係佢仲係好愛我，想繼續做我女朋友咁，但呢個msg我無覆到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家睇返，覺得當時覺得自己好幼稚，無認真諗過覆佢既每一句，每一句都係好hea咁覆，想飛人就飛人，年少無知<br />\n<br />\n係到同想飛人既講一句，唔好講一d令自己後悔既説話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5a6f6a691c44bc3512825fb8f5aea843c0e065","tid":786373,"uid":82398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:14:34.000Z","msg":"早抖"},{"pid":"b6072d8bf4dced0053a2bbfce1cab32c3b2c8990","tid":786373,"uid":112390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:15:09.000Z","msg":"唔好睇。。。"},{"pid":"84544e5473dab99354912360131ea20b278db062","tid":786373,"uid":21871,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"結果樓豬成三十歲人都冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a763a1f827044407a170ac61fe225da9914028","tid":78